# Novaya Derevnya, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Novaya Derevnya () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 60 as of 2010. There are 10 streets.
Geography
Novaya Derevnya is located  north of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Krasny Yar is the nearest rural locality.
